{"tid":1862434,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"事實證明 臨時臨急call既開花大家千其唔好信","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T16:01:42.000Z","uid":9394,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba3cdda86f8703af8a9580ef2b61f92b9e73ffc","tid":1862434,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"今日無咩特別事無啦啦call十區開花<br />\n結果就比班狗鳩拉幾件<br />\n你話好似禁蒙面法果日咁轟動既事 即晚開花就唔出奇<br />\n但今日咩都無就開花就好明顯係流野<br />\n唔單只唔好信 更加要避開<br />\n以免比班狗鳩拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外亦都證明重覆既手段唔好再用<br />\n開花，裝修，快閃<br />\n呢啲班狗都有曬對策 再做風險會好高<br />\n現階段我覺得最有用既就係全力支持醫護罷工 <br />\n再擴展到全港罷工<br />\n同時反攻中國國內輿論 話比武漢胡北甚至全個中國知中共點樣害死佢地<br />\n令佢地自我滅亡似係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed4bc13a4bba9c2708ff0817800d9c34dab5f8b","tid":1862434,"uid":91432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"便衣叫人出就個個出"},{"pid":"bbf518fc52a5395e1551c6b8235248bd2170834c","tid":1862434,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0934bc7fcb04fc18940d9335f3a63601d719ad5f","tid":1862434,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"55dd8f0993571390115a81a8d35ed72531d7c38f","tid":1862434,"uid":105340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbf518fc52a5395e1551c6b8235248bd2170834c","tid":1862434,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"因為手足信任手足"},{"pid":"4256ff924967875175a5c7f556018b4523c969a1","tid":1862434,"uid":62837,"like":1,"